div.div:
Remove required condition from date fields
This commit removes the 'required' attribute from 'products.deleted_at' field in 'ShopProductEdit.php' and the 'category.deleted_at' field in 'ShopCategoryEdit.php'. Now, these fields are optional, avoiding unnecessary input validations.

Implement Laravel Echo with chart and calendar updates
This commit integrates Laravel Echo package to enable real-time chart and calendar updates throughout the application. 'laravel-echo' was added to webpack.mix.js and its version has been updated in package.json. Necessary changes were also made to app.js, chart_controller.js , calendar_controller.js, and quill_controller.js to coordinate the delivery and reception of update messages using Laravel Echo. The overall system achieves more efficient and real-time reflection of data changes across different parts of the application.

Add PresenceEditor event and listener classes
This commit introduces the PresenceEditor event and its corresponding listener. The PresenceEditor event is designed to broadcast specific user information associated with potential editing actions. This addition aids in streamlining collaborations and managing concurrent editing scenarios.

Create PresenceEditor class and update various files
This commit introduces the new PresenceEditor class for user authorization in Broadcasting and modifies DeleteOldSales command by removing 'deleted_at' update in Console. It also enhances quill.blade.php view by adding slug data attribute and revises the animation effect in dashy.js.
